About UltraTrader-Common

A rewrite of the popular CitiTraders originally by tehBeard and tenowg.

Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
UltraTrader A rewrite of the popular CitiTraders originally by tehBeard and tenowg.
UltraTowny An Extension of UltraTrader to give Towny functionality.
UltraFactions An Extension of UltraTrader to give Faction functionality.
UltraRental An Extension of UltraTrader to allow Rental of Shops.
UltraFrame An Extension of UltraTrader to give ItemFrames to shop for display.
